name: Sales Inquiry Analysis
query:
select 
LT.name, 
LT.sales_partner, 
LT.status, 
LT.lead_name, 
LT.mobile_no, 
LT.email_id,
LT.source, 
LT.customer_group, 
LT.company_name,
LT.transaction_type,
LT.bank_name,
LT.linked_quotation,
IT.item_name, 
IT.qty
from tabLead AS LT 
INNER JOIN `tabInquiry Item` AS IT
ON LT.name = IT.parent
